title: (Mon Full) We Eliminated the First Person from the Movie Role Contention + Amy’s Son Competes in First Jiu Jitsu Tournament + Raymundo Reviews Garth Brooks’ Stadium Concert
itunes:title: (Mon Full) We Eliminated the First Person from the Movie Role Contention + Amy’s Son Competes in First Jiu Jitsu Tournament + Raymundo Reviews Garth Brooks’ Stadium Concert
description:
Someone on the show has been offered a movie role. Every day until Thursday, we will eliminate someone from the running. Today, the first show member gets the axe. Bobby recaps the events of going to Amy’s son's first Jiu Jitsu tournament. Raymundo reviews the Garth Brooks stadium concert he went to over the weekend.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
